      "title": "Help us plan the next IRE webinars!",
      "link": "https://www.ire.org/2026/07/20/help-us-plan-the-next-ire-webinars/",
      "published": "Mon, 20 Jul 2026 22:13:22 +0000",
      "summary_raw": "<p>The staff of Investigative Reporters &#38; Editors is planning the next webinars for the rest of 2026 and we want your help! If you&#8217;ve attended any webinars from IRE in the past year, we&#8217;d love it if you filled out this short survey that will help us figure out what&#8217;s most important to our members.&#8230;</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://www.ire.org/2026/07/20/help-us-plan-the-next-ire-webinars/\">Help us plan the next IRE webinars!</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://www.ire.org\">Investigative Reporters and Editors</a>.</p>",
      "source": "IRE (Investigative Reporters & Editors)"
    },
    {
