      "link": "https://wan-ifra.org/2026/07/world-press-trends-2026-27-have-your-say-on-news-industry-trends-threats-and-opportunities/",
      "published": "Tue, 21 Jul 2026 13:26:42 +0000",
      "summary_raw": "<p>Every year, publishing executives from around the world share their insights, data and projections in our annual survey and report. We are now asking news leaders to share their views to help inform the next version of our flagship report.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://wan-ifra.org/2026/07/world-press-trends-2026-27-have-your-say-on-news-industry-trends-threats-and-opportunities/\">World Press Trends 2026-27: Have your say on news industry trends, threats and opportunities</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://wan-ifra.org\">WAN-IFRA</a>.</p>",
      "source": "WAN-IFRA"
    },
